<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>9252</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>14877</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>伊坦正走向儿童中心。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>14877</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>18082</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他想象着海边。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>18082</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>21644</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，有人拍了拍他的肩膀。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>21644</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>26188</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啊！” 他吓了一跳，转过身去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>26188</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>30744</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“呃，我只是想说你好！” 波比说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>30744</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>34012</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他用手指转着篮球。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>34012</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>36199</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>伊坦叹了口气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>36199</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>40539</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我很想念放学后去冲浪的日子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>40539</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>45858</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我也很想念海边我最喜欢的墨西哥卷饼店。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>50999</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>55256</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“今天可能是你的幸运日。” 波比说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>55256</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>58907</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“雪莉老师围着围裙呢。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>58907</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>62693</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们要做什么？” 贾森问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>62693</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>66186</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他看着桌上的食材。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>66186</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>70032</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“墨西哥卷饼！” 雪莉老师说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>70032</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>72653</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>伊坦的眼睛睁大了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>72653</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>76375</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“您记得我说想做墨西哥卷饼！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>76375</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>81834</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你可以在旁边帮我。” 雪莉老师说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>81834</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>85608</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不知道怎么做。” 伊坦说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>85608</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>88728</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我只知道怎么吃！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>88728</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>91227</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大家哈哈大笑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>91227</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>95286</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“什么是墨西哥卷饼？” 尼娜问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>95286</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>99660</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>雪莉老师拿起一个墨西哥卷饼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>99660</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>105650</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“墨西哥卷饼长这样， 是一个硬硬的玉米壳。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>105650</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>109897</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你可以在里面放不同的东西。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>109897</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>112794</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“比如说？” 尼娜问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>112794</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>116322</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>雪莉老师看着伊坦。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>116322</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>123772</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗯，肉。” 他说，“豆、米饭、生菜。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>123772</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>127125</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“没错！” 雪莉老师说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>127125</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>136252</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们今天准备了碎牛肉、黑豆、米饭、生菜、芝士和莎莎酱。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>136252</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>138736</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“选你想要的食材。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>138736</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>144716</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>把食材扔进饼壳里，就可以了！” 雪莉老师说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>144716</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>149059</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“扔进饼壳里？” 波比重复说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>149059</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>153319</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是不是说我们可以把饼壳扔起来呢？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>153319</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>163114</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>像披萨一样？” 他笑着问雪莉老师。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>163114</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>167657</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不是。” 雪莉老师皱着眉说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>167657</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>169818</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不可以把东西扔起来。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>169818</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>174224</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她对伊坦说：“你要先来吗？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>174224</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>177893</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>让大家看看怎么做墨西哥卷饼！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>177893</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>185124</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“当然了！” 伊坦拿起一个饼壳。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>185124</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>190823</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“先放米饭，然后放肉。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>190823</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>197231</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这样饼壳才不会变软。” 伊坦沿着桌子走，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>197231</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>204084</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“然后加生菜。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>204084</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>208961</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我不加莎莎酱，因为我不喜欢番茄！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>208961</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>212388</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他撒了一点芝士。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>212388</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>214166</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>214166</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>219121</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“看上去挺简单的。下一个我来！” 尼娜说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>219121</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>226461</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她放了豆、米饭和莎莎酱。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>228812</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>234044</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大家做好后，拿着盘子坐到地毯上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>234044</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>237463</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦！” 莉琪大叫，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>237463</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>241103</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这个墨西哥卷饼软软的，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>241103</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>243651</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我弄得乱七八糟！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>243651</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>246646</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她的饼壳碎成两块。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>246646</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>249836</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>盘子上掉了一大块肉。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>249836</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>253488</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>连她的衣服上都有莎莎酱。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>253488</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>255959</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>尼娜咯咯笑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>255959</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>261568</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我说过不要把肉放在最下面！” 伊坦笑着说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>261568</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>269362</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>接着，大家都笑了起来，包括莉琪。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>269362</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>276214</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“墨西哥卷饼真好吃。虽然吃起来很麻烦。” 莉琪说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>276214</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>279425</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大家都准备回家了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>279425</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>285173</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谢谢你做墨西哥卷饼的建议。” 雪莉老师对伊坦说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>285173</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>287695</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这次非常成功。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>287695</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>291848</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我还有其他好想法。” 伊坦说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>291848</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>297864</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“下次我们去海边玩儿，怎么样？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>